younger woman.

544
00:37:21,200 --> 00:37:22,800
You know, age before beauty.

545
00:37:22,840 --> 00:37:24,960
- [Ruby] Oh, you're terrible.

546
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:26,480
- Oh, you love it.

547
00:37:29,200 --> 00:37:31,280
- [Gus] You look great, Ruby.

548
00:37:31,320 --> 00:37:33,320
- Very Lil Altemus,
