553
00:37:40,400 --> 00:37:41,440
- Are you kidding?

554
00:37:41,480 --> 00:37:42,600
Peach had all the credentials.

555
00:37:42,640 --> 00:37:43,760
I'm strictly middle-class.

556
00:37:43,800 --> 00:37:45,720
