00:42:15,960 --> 00:42:17,120
- Oh, no, no, it's okay.

643
00:42:17,160 --> 00:42:20,120
Juanito just got some
bad news about a friend.

644
00:42:20,160 --> 00:42:21,360
- Oh, I'm sorry.

645
00:42:21,400 --> 00:42:22,680
- So, what brings you down here?

646
00:42:22,720 --> 00:42:24,120
You wanna buy a piece of art?

647
00:42:24,160 --> 00:42:26,840
- No, I just wanted some
advice from my big brother,

648
00:42:26,880 --> 00:42:28,160
that's all.

649
00:42:28,200 --> 00:42:29,280
- Mother would never approve.

650
00:42:29,320 --> 00:42:30,600
[laughing]
- That's true.

651
00:42:31,880 --> 00:42:36,600
Um, I think I'm getting
serious about someone

652
00:42:37,480 --> 00:42:39,160
for the first time in my life.

653
00:42:40,560 --> 00:42:42,280
- Congratulations.

654
00:42:43,360 --> 00:42:45,200
Is his name Bernard Slatkin?

655
00:42:46,480 --> 00:42:47,280
- I'm afraid so.

656
00:42:48,480 --> 00:42:50,760
- And you're worried
about what she'll say?

657
00:42:51,760 --> 00:42:53,040
- I'm afraid so.

658
00:42:53,080 --> 00:42:53,560
- Don't be.

659
00:42:54,960 --> 00:42:58,200
We can't live our lives
according to Mother's rules.

660
00:42:58,240 --> 00:42:59,640
Or else we won't have any.

661
00:43:01,040 --> 00:43:03,280
And God knows life is
short enough as it is.

662
00:43:05,280 --> 00:43:07,640
- Okay, thanks, thanks.

663
00:43:07,680 --> 00:43:11,640
And tell Juanito I hope
his friend is okay, okay?

664
00:43:16,240 --> 00:43:19,520
[slow saxophone music]

665
00:43:57,200 --> 00:44:00,280
[gentle piano music]

666
00:44:17,720 --> 00:44:20,760
- It is well meant when
friends say to us,

667
00:44:20,800 --> 00:44:23,040
