670
00:44:28,880 --> 00:44:32,720
the tragedy that we have
have experienced can know.

671
00:44:34,320 --> 00:44:38,080
Someone like the total stranger
sitting next to you now.

672
00:44:39,560 --> 00:44:44,560
That person can understand
our feelings of anger or rage.

673
00:44:46,760 --> 00:44:50,600
But feelings, no matter
what they are,

674
00:44:50,640 --> 00:44:53,000
