translated them into action.

678
00:45:04,560 --> 00:45:05,600
- What about justice?

679
00:45:08,600 --> 00:45:09,600
My daughter is dead,

680
00:45:11,440 --> 00:45:13,800
but the man who murdered
her is still alive,

681
00:45:15,320 --> 00:45:17,000
and the only
punishment he received

682
