the victim do not equate

685
00:45:29,920 --> 00:45:31,120
with the rights of the criminal.

686
00:45:31,160 --> 00:45:32,560
- That's true, and I think that

687
00:45:32,600 --> 00:45:34,680
that's something we should
all work very hard to change.

688
00:45:34,720 --> 00:45:36,520
- We have to change it.

689
00:45:36,560 --> 00:45:38,000
