2015
02:03:23,320 --> 02:03:25,560
[laughing]

2016
02:03:28,880 --> 02:03:32,040
[electrical fizzling]

2017
02:03:34,280 --> 02:03:35,440
- Oh.

2018
02:03:35,480 --> 02:03:36,320
Oh.

2019
02:03:38,800 --> 02:03:41,960
[electrical fizzling]

2020
02:03:46,920 --> 02:03:50,080
[electrical fizzling]

2021
02:03:52,720 --> 02:03:54,680
