2022
02:03:54,720 --> 02:03:57,960
[electrical fizzling]

2023
02:03:58,000 --> 02:03:59,280
- The lights.

2024
02:03:59,320 --> 02:04:00,120
The lights.

2025
02:04:00,160 --> 02:04:00,960
The lights!

2026
02:04:01,000 --> 02:04:01,800
Turn out the lights!

2027
02:04:01,840 --> 02:04:03,800
Turn out the lights!

2028
02:04:03,840 --> 02:04:05,880
[electrical fizzling]

2029
02:04:05,920 --> 02:04:07,360
- Let me out of here.

2030
02:04:07,400 --> 02:04:10,240
[crowd commotion]

2031
02:04:15,880 --> 02:04:18,720
- I was talking about
the chandeliers, damn it!

2032
02:04:18,760 --> 02:04:19,560
Turn the lights back on!

2033
02:04:19,600 --> 02:04:21,200
- I can't find the switch.

2034
02:04:21,240 --> 02:04:22,680
- How could you have
let this happen?

2035
02:04:22,720 --> 02:04:25,080
- You're the one that
wanted all this!

